title: No. 9 Tech downed by New Mexico - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: No. 9 Tech downed by New Mexico - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: ALBUQUERQUE, N.M. – New Mexico connected for a three-run walk-off home run in the bottom of the ninth to hand No. 9 Texas Tech an 11-10 loss on Tuesday afternoon at Santa Ana Star Field. The Lobos scored four runs in the last frame in the comeback effort and pushed the Red Raiders' losing streak to five.
